high_descs: Go over to sink
Pick up knife out of sink
Go to microwave on right
Open microwave on the counter
Place knife in microwave
Pick up slice of tomato to the right of microwave
Go over to refrigerator
Open refrigerator, place tomato on top left shelf, close refrigerator, open refrigerator, grab tomato, close refrigerator door
Go to counter with coffee maker, green cup
Place tomato on counter in front of coffee maker
anns.task_desc: Put away knife, slice, chill tomato, put tomato on counter

high_descs: Turn right, go straight, at the chair turn right, go past the counter, bear straight and left to the sink.
Take the knife in the sink.
Turn left to face the microwave.
Cut the tomato on the counter to the right of the microwave.
Put the knife in the microwave.
Take a slice of tomato from the counter.
Turn around, go to the fridge.
Put the tomato in the freezer on the left side of the fridge. Close and open the fridge doors. Take the tomato from the fridge.
Go to the counter to the left of the fridge where the coffee machine is.
Put the tomato in front of the coffee machine on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a frozen tomato slice on a counter.

high_descs: Turn right, walk to the counter, turn right, walk past the counter, turn left, walk to the stove, turn right, and walk to the sink.
Pick up the knife.
Turn left towards the microwave.
Slice the tomato on the counter.
Put the knife in the microwave.
Pick up a tomato slice.
Turn around and cross the room to the fridge.
Put the tomato slice in the fridge. Take the tomato slice out of the fridge.
Turn left, head to the coffee pot, and turn right.
Put the tomato slice on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold tomato slice on the counter.

high_descs: Turn and go to the kitchen sink.
Pick up the knife that is in the kitchen sink.
With the knife turn towards the microwave to your left.
Slice the tomato that is to the right of the microwave. While holding the knife open the microwave door that is on the counter.
Place the knife in the microwave in front of the cup that is in there and across the plate.
Pick up the tomato slice that is to the right of the microwave.
With the tomato slice in hand turn all the way around and go to the fridge.
Open the fridge.  Place the tomato slice on the top left shelf.  Close the fridge.  Open the fridge and grab the tomato slice that is on the top left shelf.
Turn and go to the coffee maker that is next to the green cup.
Place the tomato slice to the left of the green cup and in front of the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Slice a tomato to put on the counter.
